    <item>
      <title>[工具] LaTex</title>
      <link>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/latex/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/latex/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[工具] LaTex</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="报告模版">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%8a%a5%e5%91%8a%e6%a8%a1%e7%89%88"></a>
报告模版
</h1><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-tex" data-lang="tex"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 1. 基础文档与中文支持（Overleaf专用，修复生僻字）
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\documentclass</span><span class="na">[UTF8,fontset=none]</span><span class="nb">{</span>ctexart<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% Overleaf 原生预装 Noto 思源字体，完整支持“焜”等生僻字
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\setCJKmainfont</span><span class="nb">{</span>Noto Serif CJK SC<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\setCJKsansfont</span><span class="nb">{</span>Noto Sans CJK SC<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">\setCJKmonofont</span><span class="nb">{</span>Noto Sans Mono CJK SC<span class="nb">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% ==============================
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c">% 2. 页面布局与边距设置
